node.text:
I bought this watch from the grandson of the original owner.  He was able to provide a short but interesting history about this rare Constellation watch. “My grandfather is from Transylvania (when it belonged to Hungary). He is a Magyar. He ended up being very big in Romanian politics and was in prison for many years as a political prisoner. He helped liberate Romania from the Iron Guard. He and my grandmother actually met in prison, my grandmother was jailed at a very early age. He remained in Romania all his life until his death in the late 80's.” .
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
